	<h1>Sand Saves</h1>
	<p>For sand saves, we need to know whether you played from a greenside bunker then holed the ball with 1 putt. You don't need to have made par for a sand save to count.</p>
	<p>&nbsp;</p>
	<h2>Entering your data</h2>
	<div class="floatEnder"></div>	
	<div style="float: left; width: 124px; margin-right: 10px;">
		<p><img class="imgBorder" src="/tracker/wl/lovegolf/images/im-help-sand-none.gif" height="47" width="122" alt="Sand save not attempted" /></p>
	</div>
	<div style="float: right; width: 400px;">
		<p>If you <strong>didn't attempt</strong> a sand save, leave the checkbox <strong>unticked</strong>. The other options are unselectable and you are done.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="floatEnder"></div>
	<p>&nbsp;</p>
	<div style="float: left; width: 124px; margin-right: 10px;">
		<p><img class="imgBorder" src="/tracker/wl/lovegolf/images/im-help-sand-miss.gif" height="47" width="122" alt="Sand save missed" /></p>
	</div>
	<div style="float: right; width: 400px;">
		<p>If you <strong>attempted but failed to hit</strong> a sand save, click the checkbox to tick it. Then choose 'Miss' from the drop-down menu.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="floatEnder"></div>
	<p>&nbsp;</p>
	<div style="float: left; width: 124px; margin-right: 10px;">
		<p><img class="imgBorder" src="/tracker/wl/lovegolf/images/im-help-sand-hit.gif" height="47" width="122" alt="Sand save hit" /></p>
	</div>
	<div style="float: right; width: 400px;">
		<p>If you <strong>attempted and hit</strong> a sand save, click the checkbox to tick it. Then choose 'Hit' from the drop-down menu.</p>
	</div>
